// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0270 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 85b945e5-254b-5255-9df5-791f20d6aab7

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
